<p><a href="https://github.com/MaoLongLong/bytebufferpool/blob/main/pool_bench_test.go">pool_bench_test.go</a></p>
<p>从上往下，分别为 ByteBufferPool, MinIO BytePoolCap 和普通 <code>[]byte</code></p>






<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#cdd6f4;background-color:#1e1e2e;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>$ go <span style="color:#89dceb">test</span> -bench<span style="color:#89dceb;font-weight:bold">=</span>Pool -benchmem
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>goos: linux
